{"tid":1630990,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[道德撚、左膠黑色警告] 邊有人咁撚戇鳩, 有黑警臥底呢張皇牌都唔用, 乜鳩都主動攬撚哂上身","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:23:54.000Z","uid":34241,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"42f0f46292ea8da047438e8d170e79f028fc8a95","tid":1630990,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:20:30.000Z","msg":"幾個月以黎一直都影到好多黑警、便衣著黑衫, <br />\nfull gear (有d仲靚過普通文具), 著示威者裝束假扮示威者既證據,<br />\n有d帶頭搞事, 有d勸留, 有d開埋實彈, 有d玩埋火魔法, 有d出盡力裝修<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">偏偏「對左膠恨之入骨既連登仔」之中居然有人戇鳩到乜撚野都攬哂上身</span>,<br />\n有事唔係第一時間質疑臥底, <br />\n居然第一時間「代前線道歉」<br />\n<br />\n一黎你<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>冇證冇據</strong></span></span>就<span style=\"color: red;\">屈自己友</span>, <br />\n未問過前線就主動代人道歉, <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">格硬質自己友食死貓</span>, <br />\n前線有口難言,<br />\n好難有人返黎開post 比證據講返單野唔係自己友做<br />\n變左冇撚得解釋<br />\n<br />\n二黎你知唔知你呢句道歉即係等於<span style=\"color: red;\">光速割蓆</span>, (不論示威者有冇做過) <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第一時間劃清界線,<br />\n搶佔道德高地</span>, <br />\n表示「我地有道德唔會做呢d野, 前線做錯左 我代佢道歉, 下次唔會」<br />\n咁樣係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>赤裸裸既出賣</strong></span>, 同幾年前班飯民、割蓆撚有乜撚野分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果我係黑警阿頭就即刻派一半兵力全力扮示威者搞事,<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打砸搶燒, 無差別攻擊, 當街當巷強姦,<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反正呢班道德潔癖既連登仔/左膠/打手全部都會問都唔問就攬哂上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甚至有證據證明到黑警偽裝示威者搞事, 呢班人會全部當睇唔到, 即時潛哂水<br />\n<br />\nlink就唔貼了, 自己睇下熱門果幾個post, 出奇地多正評<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>維穩機器開始進化, 識得用返2014左膠既招數黎攻陷返2019既連登仔</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"663dc50110993bbce2a6cde59177b04f3bca6711","tid":1630990,"uid":6891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:22:46.000Z","msg":"推呀屌 唔要被道歉<br />\n要道歉就自己落場做完先道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5dae3965a83156062be0f9dfc1ff7412a1316ef","tid":1630990,"uid":34241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:05:15.000Z","msg":"第一時間認罪, 冇人會讚你叻仔<br />\n有都唔會多過兩秒<br />\n但你主動認罪, 之後就算有證據唔係你做, 都已經打唔甩,<br />\n你已經成功親手將一個暴徒既形象種左係大眾心入面<br />\n<br />\n無間謀戰, 咁簡單既技巧都唔識,<br />\n學咩人玩文宣戰"},{"pid":"1b2acef5196406bb5b5b4fc6e14b9470d5b32f98","tid":1630990,"uid":59800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:06:14.000Z","msg":"手足邊有咁on9呀 好明顯你黑警做架啦"},{"pid":"7eb6b5b220290ca5e4b85943d09f2152d8a2e5ec","tid":1630990,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:06:14.000Z","msg":"叫果啲撚屌自首啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又話無大台"},{"pid":"81171e57c8a8ebdf61b4469179653393ac7cdbfa","tid":1630990,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:06:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"943707c0b4d4d537d5667e2e727382595a811fe4","tid":1630990,"uid":239911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:07:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a745fbc00d722047d347131925831f4e6b01d1a","tid":1630990,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:07:32.000Z","msg":"無撚錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c47273557a615dc1ad19ba91ac1e15baf92252","tid":1630990,"uid":87780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:09:16.000Z","msg":"班人係根本有心帶風向既左膠嚟<br />\n只係會分化同批鬥自己人"},{"pid":"9b55053325f18c21f95b7aeb7cbe5ce58523c920","tid":1630990,"uid":184581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:09:59.000Z","msg":"一有人掉火魔法<br />\n一有人私了<br />\n一有人破壞野<br />\n第一時間衝出黎<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫前線認罪</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nD人話佢唔好咁快認係自己友做就話你 分化, 想捉鬼"},{"pid":"1e77a3efcad9b52bbd62c3265bb425e19a307229","tid":1630990,"uid":183758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9b55053325f18c21f95b7aeb7cbe5ce58523c920","tid":1630990,"uid":184581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:09:59.000Z","msg":"一有人掉火魔法<br />\n一有人私了<br />\n一有人破壞野<br />\n第一時間衝出黎<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫前線認罪</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nD人話佢唔好咁快認係自己友做就話你 分化, 想捉鬼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:10:47.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"77e4c5151c35b5f1053e7fb48d6862909d8e15af","tid":1630990,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01c47273557a615dc1ad19ba91ac1e15baf92252","tid":1630990,"uid":87780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:09:16.000Z","msg":"班人係根本有心帶風向既左膠嚟<br />\n只係會分化同批鬥自己人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:10:58.000Z","msg":"無撚錯"},{"pid":"f6a2000b5c62f9e1c3d617e90a57a73a554dc2dc","tid":1630990,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:13:57.000Z","msg":"出post果個有心帶風向，用個好靚好正義既門面引人落搭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入世未深既連登仔又中多次伏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不得不說對家既維穩機器個大腦真係相當強勁<br />\n立場飄少少都比佢陰到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78bff463614f863e75d9d8e668298d6b7dd19141","tid":1630990,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:16:32.000Z","msg":"第一時間搶住認班人一查就知係0 post狗acc"},{"pid":"4dce1ec204e63911d3612e1106c3bd885b1bbaea","tid":1630990,"uid":195950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:17:54.000Z","msg":"但係萬一有人唔自律<br />\n濫用黑警臥底嘅名義咁點"},{"pid":"94b3d77c91d6c5ba74a595aad846c931bfe82745","tid":1630990,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:19:23.000Z","msg":"咁鍾意代人道歉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都代黑警多謝連登仔幫手包底，我地D臥底穿哂煲都冇人追住黎屌，多謝哂大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82891c83f908ca1d5e7705883a57abaaa89b2c57","tid":1630990,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:03:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8350ec9d674ce81c6c9a58a344ddb4de80a670a5","tid":1630990,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:08:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對於有記者因汽油彈受傷<br />\n香港人及抗爭者深表遺憾<br />\n然而根據以往經驗,警察多次派出臥底假扮抗爭者故意向記者投擲汽油彈<br />\n而本日之抗爭中發現警察派出臥底甚多<br />\n現階段未能確定為警察臥底投擲,或為抗爭者誤中記者<br />\n雖現場抗爭者即時為中彈記者撲火,然而亦無法確定記者之傷勢情況<br />\n現抗爭者向中彈記者致以慰問及望記者能早日康復<br />\n綞調查後如發現為抗爭者誤中記者,抗爭者將致以最衷心之道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n並會確切反省,以期望日後不會再發生同樣錯誤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一眾香港人及抗爭者</blockquote><br />\n咁講又得唔得？"},{"pid":"779dcdb87545f373e428160d36932eeeb6452cbc","tid":1630990,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8350ec9d674ce81c6c9a58a344ddb4de80a670a5","tid":1630990,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:08:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對於有記者因汽油彈受傷<br />\n香港人及抗爭者深表遺憾<br />\n然而根據以往經驗,警察多次派出臥底假扮抗爭者故意向記者投擲汽油彈<br />\n而本日之抗爭中發現警察派出臥底甚多<br />\n現階段未能確定為警察臥底投擲,或為抗爭者誤中記者<br />\n雖現場抗爭者即時為中彈記者撲火,然而亦無法確定記者之傷勢情況<br />\n現抗爭者向中彈記者致以慰問及望記者能早日康復<br />\n綞調查後如發現為抗爭者誤中記者,抗爭者將致以最衷心之道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n並會確切反省,以期望日後不會再發生同樣錯誤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一眾香港人及抗爭者</blockquote><br />\n咁講又得唔得？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:22:59.000Z","msg":"第2句之後加呢段, 成為一段完整既發言 (起碼讀3分鐘)：<br />\n<br />\n「過去幾月警察多次作出<span style=\"color: red;\">針對性</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">主動攻擊</span>記者及FA既行為,<br />\n包括多次<span style=\"color: red;\">刻意</span>以大光燈、閃燈照射記者雙眼、拍攝器材,<br />\n以恐嚇、人牆、盾牌<span style=\"color: red;\">阻礙拍攝</span>,<br />\n數十人圍困幾名記者, <span style=\"color: red;\">無合理解釋下主動推撞、攻擊、搜查</span>記者,<br />\n向無任何示威者、無威脅既記者群投擲、發射催淚彈,<br />\n甚至<span style=\"color: red;\">扯低其防毒面罩、向面部、眼睛近距離噴射催淚氣體</span>,<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我地嚴重懷疑呢D種種行為係警隊有意針對第四權既有組織有計劃恐怖襲擊</strong></span>,<br />\n對於警隊公然襲擊記者表示強烈譴責」<br />\n<br />\n(可以講埋國際戰爭都唔會咁樣對記者, 可見香港警隊已經全面失控, 犯下既戰爭罪行比阿蓋達、ISIS更嚴重)"},{"pid":"bcffbc521c3e722206d9cd5c30bd37061329a169","tid":1630990,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"779dcdb87545f373e428160d36932eeeb6452cbc","tid":1630990,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8350ec9d674ce81c6c9a58a344ddb4de80a670a5","tid":1630990,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:08:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對於有記者因汽油彈受傷<br />\n香港人及抗爭者深表遺憾<br />\n然而根據以往經驗,警察多次派出臥底假扮抗爭者故意向記者投擲汽油彈<br />\n而本日之抗爭中發現警察派出臥底甚多<br />\n現階段未能確定為警察臥底投擲,或為抗爭者誤中記者<br />\n雖現場抗爭者即時為中彈記者撲火,然而亦無法確定記者之傷勢情況<br />\n現抗爭者向中彈記者致以慰問及望記者能早日康復<br />\n綞調查後如發現為抗爭者誤中記者,抗爭者將致以最衷心之道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n並會確切反省,以期望日後不會再發生同樣錯誤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一眾香港人及抗爭者</blockquote><br />\n咁講又得唔得？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:22:59.000Z","msg":"第2句之後加呢段, 成為一段完整既發言 (起碼讀3分鐘)：<br />\n<br />\n「過去幾月警察多次作出<span style=\"color: red;\">針對性</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">主動攻擊</span>記者及FA既行為,<br />\n包括多次<span style=\"color: red;\">刻意</span>以大光燈、閃燈照射記者雙眼、拍攝器材,<br />\n以恐嚇、人牆、盾牌<span style=\"color: red;\">阻礙拍攝</span>,<br />\n數十人圍困幾名記者, <span style=\"color: red;\">無合理解釋下主動推撞、攻擊、搜查</span>記者,<br />\n向無任何示威者、無威脅既記者群投擲、發射催淚彈,<br />\n甚至<span style=\"color: red;\">扯低其防毒面罩、向面部、眼睛近距離噴射催淚氣體</span>,<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>